303
00:40:23,059 --> 00:40:25,079
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se čujemo, Sara, Boži ti blagoslov.

304
00:40:25,079 --> 00:40:26,059
[SPEAKER_01] Može.

305
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:30,719
[SPEAKER_01] Bog, Bog. Dora, ti si htjela možda podvući još nešto malo oko ovog izlazga?

306
00:40:30,719 --> 00:40:39,659
